FF7Z5Fc2bewCEw/s1600/mapa_comarcas_f.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="200" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-uN_HYmZExcc/V46ckIlGtoI/AAAAAAAADSU/mDZK0bcO0B8WJaHo3qI3VjFF7Z5Fc2bewCEw/s200/mapa_comarcas_f.jpg" width="160" /></a><br />En la muestra se pudieron &nbsp;ver hasta 70 muñecos vestidos de ribereños, serranos, montañeses, danzantes...<br /><span style="text-align: center;">Con vestimentas &nbsp;sorprendentes, y muy diferentes de una comarca a otra, la</span>&nbsp;indumentaria tradicional es elemento de identidad y manifestación cultural de los pueblos.<br /><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-bWBOXJIIs0Q/V45ZrU1NKgI/AAAAAAAADRk/LVeNestM2vcTwfMgL0GN5l-5oftVX2MCwCLcB/s1600/expo%2B34%2B19-07.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="640" src="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-bWBOXJIIs0Q/V45ZrU1NKgI/AAAAAAAADRk/LVeNestM2vcTwfMgL0GN5l-5oftVX2MCwCLcB/s640/expo%2B34%2B19-07.jpg" width="534" /></a></div><br /><br /><div><div style="text-align: left;"><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"></div><a href="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-k9cM4OlBzpo/V45OYxgyHvI/AAAAAAAADP8/sbsfT5WUFxQKGnixwxKSc3dreCKJdGZkQCLcB/s1600/expo%2B1a%2B19-07.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="510" src="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-k9cM4OlBzpo/V45OYxgyHvI/AAAAAAAADP8/sbsfT5WUFxQKGnixwxKSc3dreCKJdGZkQCLcB/s640/expo%2B1a%2B19-07.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><br /><a href="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-xjQn-Wq9xgI/V45QxHmKHeI/AAAAAAAADQs/qWiCKXo2MVQd5wbesSi2S3sc0MOgQ4pXgCLcB/s1600/expo%2B3%2B19-07.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: center;"><img border="0" height="626" src="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-xjQn-Wq9xgI/V45QxHmKHeI/AAAAAAAADQs/q