://2.bp.blogspot.com/-8P2VVU4wxWk/V31ug8dFm0I/AAAAAAAADMc/0jNUqJjZcy8du5FC26gB_4bCd22YU1QUQCLcB/s1600/exposici%25C3%25B3n%2B2016%2B12.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="408" src="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-8P2VVU4wxWk/V31ug8dFm0I/AAAAAAAADMc/0jNUqJjZcy8du5FC26gB_4bCd22YU1QUQCLcB/s640/exposici%25C3%25B3n%2B2016%2B12.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><span style="text-align: justify;">Ya clausurada, la exposición ha sido muy visitada. Sin ir más lejos, el primer día, coincidiendo con la "Noche Blanca", pasaron alrededor de unas 4600 personas.</span><br /><span style="text-align: justify;">Para aquellos que no pudieron acudir aquí dejamos una galería de fotos para que, aunque no sea en directo, también puedan&nbsp;contemplar&nbsp;los distintos trajes expuestos.</span><br /><div><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="text-align: start;"><br /></span></div><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="text-align: start;">Prendas masculinas de abrigo: Capa castellana</span></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-VllbWZnG6bU/V3rEoy1vKiI/AAAAAAAADJc/fqAKIeEToyI2RghjTdAA3-gprNKgRGncgCLcB/s1600/exposicion%2B5.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="400" src="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-VllbWZnG6bU/V3rEoy1vKiI/AAAAAAAADJc/fqAKIeEToyI2RghjTdAA3-gprNKgRGncgCLcB/s400/exposicion%2B5.jpg" width="300" /></a></div><a href="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-8JOlW2yayqQ/V3rEodJWSfI/AAAAAAAADJY/GorUTN052OUOVKoelgSV4ljECRafxf4pwCLcB/s1600/exposici%25C3%25B3n%2B6.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: right; float: right; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em; text-align: center;"><img border="0" height="400" src="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-8JOlW2yayqQ/V3rEodJWSfI/AAAAAAAADJY/GorUTN052OUOVKoelgSV4ljECRafxf4pwCLcB/s400/exposici%25C3%25B3n%2B6.jpg" width="300" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <br /><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="text-align: start;"><br /></span></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: left;"><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: left;">Prendas femenina de abrigo: Pelerina de lana, tejida a mano</div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: left;"><a href="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-cbJkPa55F-E/V3rGZQFHvjI/AAAAAAAADJs/petcJpz81OEr0Oq_YNc-K8BMuKjdWUCiQCLcB/s1600/exposici%25C3%25B3n%2B2016%2B7.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="318" src="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-cbJkPa55F-E/V3rGZQFHvjI/AAAAAAAADJs/petcJpz81OEr0Oq_YNc-K8BMuKjdWUCiQCLcB/s320/exposici%25C3%25B3n%2B2016%2B7.jpg" width="320" /></a><a href="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-r4WB2FoLn48/V3rGXZQwyPI/AAAAAAAADJo/AfXlt4q3YRo7EusZPwgcFJuOsv7Z5ivRQCLcB/s1600/exposici%25C3%25B3n%2B2016%2B8.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: center;"><img border="0" height="320" src="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-r4WB2FoLn48/V3rGXZQwyPI/AAAAAAAADJo/AfXlt4q3YRo7EusZPwgcFJuOsv7Z5ivRQCLcB/s320/exposici%25C3%25B3n%2B2016%2B8.jpg" width="276" /></a></div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <br /><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-fja7WUygJnA/V3rICc1WxiI/AAAAAAAADJ4/jHMvvgwBKCQiMVex1QQWZmX_i2dapZDWwCLcB/s1600/taller%2Bde%2Bcostura.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: left;"><img border="0" height="640" src="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-fja7WUygJnA/V3rICc1WxiI/AAAAAAAADJ4/jHMvvgwBKCQiMVex1QQWZmX_i2dapZDWwCLcB/s640/taller%2Bde%2Bcostura.jpg" width="425" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="text-align: start;">Taller de costura y plancha</span></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><br /></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: small; line-height: normal;"><br /></span></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ZE7O8Sb_LJM/V3q2cp2rNaI/AAAAAAAADI8/FzFtuYlbgJ4WlbXxqNiT2Amg0vtmitWeQCLcB/s1600/exposicion%2B2016%2B1.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="486" src="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ZE7O8Sb_LJM/V3q2cp2rNaI/AAAAAAAADI8/FzFtuYlbgJ4WlbXxqNiT2Amg0vtmitWeQCLcB/s640/exposicion%2B2016%2B1.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><div>Una de las fiestas más populares y de más tradición en la provincia de Burgos, y que todavía se conservan en el siglo XXI, son las Romerías, que se celebran en la mayoría de los pueblos y también en Burgos capital.<br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-FrlTrhXnTUE/V3rKh4nxRXI/AAAAAAAADKI/bKkoypz0nowBP2pEeB5b4mG7WXaQZ6CVQCLcB/s1600/exposici%25C3%25B3n%2B2016%2B11.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="478" src="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-FrlTrhXnTUE/V3rKh4nxRXI/AAAAAAAADKI/bKkoypz0nowBP2pEeB5b4mG7WXaQZ6CVQCLcB/s640/exposici%25C3%25B3n%2B2016%2B11.jpg" width="640" /></a></div></div><div><br /><br /></div><div><a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-0YSkGdRzcOg/V3q6q-0xlCI/AAAAAAAADJI/7QryZuzEoWc1fI6U3_M0zbBi9KGLaoEQACLcB/s1600/exposicion%2B2016%2B2jpg.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: center;"><img border="0" height="355" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-0YSkGdRzcOg/V3q6q-0xlCI/AAAAAAAADJI/7QryZuzEoWc1fI6U3_M0zbBi9KGLaoEQACLcB/s400/exposicion%2B2016%2B2jpg.jpg" width="400" /></a></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <br /><br /><br /><br /><div style="text-align: right;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-yWFAloWEFak/V35wKQjX2pI/AAAAAAAADMw/E8Wh0sHxNHEWOYjUa9AGdu4h_Tm5WGBfACLcB/s1600/exposicion%2B2016%2B11.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: center;"><img border="0" height="151" src="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-yWFAloWEFak/V35wKQjX2pI/AAAAAAAADMw/E8Wh0sHxNHEWOYjUa9AGdu4h_Tm5WGBfACLcB/s200/exposicion%2B2016%2B11.jpg" width="200" /></a></div></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: left;"><a href="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-FvvfKIPYNug/V35wxxt89-I/AAAAAAAADM8/jny2lkSURPYnfC2NZpSJpWN9qzpdjxhuwCLcB/s1600/exposicion%2B2016%2B13.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: right; float: right; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em;"><img border="0" height="288" src="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-FvvfKIPYNug/V35wxxt89-I/AAAAAAAADM8/jny2lkSURPYnfC2NZpSJpWN9qzpdjxhuwCLcB/s320/exposicion%2B2016%2B13.jpg" width="320" /></a><a href="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-XZq6gUXPzsU/V35wKwrM7qI/AAAAAAAADM0/Yd9fLalu8XoK0oPLRpexrGvZV2hxNK8rACLcB/s1600/exposicion%2B2016%2B12.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: center;"><img border="0" height="320" src="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-XZq6gUXPzsU/V35wKwrM7qI/AAAAAAAADM0/Yd9fLalu8XoK0oPLRpexrGvZV2hxNK8rACLcB/s320/exposicion%2B2016%2B12.jpg" width="256" /></a></div><div style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: center;"><span style="text-align: justify;"><br /></span></div><div style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: center;"><span style="text-align: justify;">BODA TRADICIONAL CASTELLANA</span></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-rjmmuG4vXnI/V4z3qO54crI/AAAAAAAADPE/9DdVhvsfto8SknTaRifLLajh9FJM4gunwCEw/s1600/exposicion%2Bboda%2B2016%2B125.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="238" src="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-rjmmuG4vXnI/V4z3qO54crI/AAAAAAAADPE/9DdVhvsfto8SknTaRifLLajh9FJM4gunwCEw/s640/exposicion%2Bboda%2B2016%2B125.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><div style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: left;">"Con un sí que dio la novia a la puerta de la iglesia con un si que dio la novia entró libre y salió presa."</div><div class="separator" style="clear: both;"></div><div style="text-align: center;"><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-1lRAGl5R8pQ/V4z-nV3PBkI/AAAAAAAADPQ/32IPnl502EcQvdXqS8C4dk3N2bJ700FoACEw/s1600/exposicion%2B2016%2Bboda%2B1.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="483" src="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-1lRAGl5R8pQ/V4z-nV3PBkI/AAAAAAAADPQ/32IPnl502EcQvdXqS8C4dk3N2bJ700FoACEw/s640/exposicion%2B2016%2Bboda%2B1.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Y3B5vHUxbrk/V4z-rTf6KfI/AAAAAAAADPY/xjra8FhG0E8SCTBkzzcaeLPx-l7s2eaVwCEw/s1600/exposicion%2B2016%2Binvitados%2B1.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: right; float: right; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em;"><img border="0" height="305" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Y3B5vHUxbrk/V4z-rTf6KfI/AAAAAAAADPY/xjra8FhG0E8SCTBkzzcaeLPx-l7s2eaVwCEw/s400/exposicion%2B2016%2Binvitados%2B1.jpg" width="400" /></a><br /><div style="text-align: left;"><br /></div><div style="text-align: left;">"Que bonita está la sierra con el tomillo florido&nbsp;</div></div>más bonita está la novia <br />del brazo de su marido"</div><div><br /></div><div>"Crezca el honor de la espiga y el trigo <br />crezca el honor de novios y padrinos <br />crezca el honor de los mozos y mozas <br />crezca el honor de la espina y la rosa. "</div><div><br /><i>Estrofas del canto al honor de nuevo mester de juglaría</i><br />------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"></div><a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-uN_HYmZExcc/V46ckIlGtoI/AAAAAAAADSU/mDZK0bcO0B8WJaHo3qI3VjFF7Z5Fc2bewCEw/s1600/mapa_comarcas_f.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="200" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-uN_HYmZExcc/V46ckIlGtoI/AAAAAAAADSU/mDZK0bcO0B8WJaHo3qI3VjFF7Z5Fc2bewCEw/s200/mapa_comarcas_f.jpg" width="160" /></a><br />En la muestra se pudieron &nbsp;ver hasta 70 muñecos vestidos de ribereños, serranos, montañeses, danzantes...<br /><span style="text-align: center;">Con vestimentas &nbsp;sorprendentes, y muy diferentes de una comarca a otra, la</span>&nbsp;indumentaria tradicional es elemento de identidad y manifestación cultural de los pueblos.<br /><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-bWBOXJIIs0Q/V45ZrU1NKgI/AAAAAAAADRk/LVeNestM2vcTwfMgL0GN5l-5oftVX2MCwCLcB/s1600/expo%2B34%2B19-07.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="640" src="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-bWBOXJIIs0Q/V45ZrU1NKgI/AAAAAAAADRk/LVeNestM2vcTwfMgL0GN5l-5oftVX2MCwCLcB/s640/expo%2B34%2B19-07.jpg" width="534" /></a></div><br /><br /><div><div style="text-align: left;"><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"></div><a href="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-k9cM4OlBzpo/V45OYxgyHvI/AAAAAAAADP8/sbsfT5WUFxQKGnixwxKSc3dreCKJdGZkQCLcB/s1600/expo%2B1a%2B19-07.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="510" src="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-k9cM4OlBzpo/V45OYxgyHvI/AAAAAAAADP8/sbsfT5WUFxQKGnixwxKSc3dreCKJdGZkQCLcB/s640/expo%2B1a%2B19-07.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><br /><a href="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-xjQn-Wq9xgI/V45QxHmKHeI/AAAAAAAADQs/qWiCKXo2MVQd5wbesSi2S3sc0MOgQ4pXgCLcB/s1600/expo%2B3%2B19-07.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: center;"><img border="0" height="626" src="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-xjQn-Wq9xgI/V45QxHmKHeI/AAAAAAAADQs/qWiCKXo2MVQd5wbesSi2S3sc0MOgQ4pXgCLcB/s640/expo%2B3%2B19-07.jpg" width="640" /></a><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-DWsQKis1e24/V45ObmtfdxI/AAAAAAAADQA/CvojD_DUHuknRM9zkBaacvN41lbH-YVbgCLcB/s1600/expo%2B%2B2%2B19-07.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="352" src="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-DWsQKis1e24/V45ObmtfdxI/AAAAAAAADQA/CvojD_DUHuknRM9zkBaacvN41lbH-YVbgCLcB/s640/expo%2B%2B2%2B19-07.jpg" width="640" /></a><a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ew5R9oDb7xY/V45OOYoRBPI/AAAAAAAADP4/TiwwbBgQE0MyqKnK0HYd32YEicp1I-2MQCLcB/s1600/expo%2B1%2B19-07.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: right; float: right; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em;"><img border="0" height="314" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ew5R9oDb7xY/V45OOYoRBPI/AAAAAAAADP4/TiwwbBgQE0MyqKnK0HYd32YEicp1I-2MQCLcB/s640/expo%2B1%2B19-07.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><br /><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Blfoe3XbeDQ/V45RsALcUSI/AAAAAAAADQ0/slbpXZ-vR78K65xgzyCV48CQn0MoQDLHwCLcB/s1600/expo%2B5%2B19-07.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: right; float: right; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em; text-align: right;"><img border="0" height="640" src="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Blfoe3XbeDQ/V45RsALcUSI/AAAAAAAADQ0/slbpXZ-vR78K65xgzyCV48CQn0MoQDLHwCLcB/s640/expo%2B5%2B19-07.jpg" width="620" /></a><a href="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Xrl6obaGifg/V45Rx2nUJLI/AAAAAAAADQ8/svWjOKw-xKEO5hMjCuC3e_OoQW3zVCecgCLcB/s1600/expo%2B4%2B19-07.jpg" imageanchor="1" s